libexadrums (0.5.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream version.
    Rename the library version because of the new Shared Object version.
    New dependency on libminizip.
  * Depend on zlib1g-dev because libminizip-dev does not.
  * Select Debian branch in Vcs-Browser.
  * Swap binary packages in control files in order to avoid hard-coding
    the SO version in the packaging.
  * Debhelper 13.  Refine patterns in debhelper config files.
  * Drop obsolete work-around for libtool bug.
  * Mark autopkgtests as superficial.
  * Add upstream/metadata.
  * Standards-Version 4.5.1 (no changes)

 -- Jeremy Oden <jerem.oden@gmail.com>  Sat, 28 Nov 2020 17:25:26 +0100

